Reference: Government Decision No. HTED-29066 (11) / 11/2024/810617 -MHT- (HE-4), d. 15.07.2024.

As per the Government decision, new subjects / courses, additional batches, new faculty have been approved under extension in the existing colleges for the academic year 2024-2025. However, the respective universities and institutions have requested for modification of the said approval order. Accordingly, the University's Recommendation B documents were examined. The amendment mentioned in the following statement is being approved by the Government as it is required to be amended in accordance with the said inspection.
